Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（真有种啊  瑛里华）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,270)\fad(800,0)\fs26}开学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你放她鸽子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  我只是去晚了  副会长已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是放鸽子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又平白无故地增加说对不起的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不是按班级固定位置的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你待会就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从今天起的这一学年  就是我最后的一个学年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与心爱的你们共有的时间  只有这仅仅的一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我要让这一年成为最精彩的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  我将不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是择下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来  之前应该是他特有的玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是我  而是在场的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们创造最精彩的一年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的各位  你们燃起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后排的各位  给点力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼的  我们是一条心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齐心合力拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这人气还真是惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  别看他那样  他要做起事来还是很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真主角登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长说话吵了点  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这话有点唐突
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想问问  诸位看见这手了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手有点冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看  难道不觉得它很寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是这样觉得的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就牵着我的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别的人也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和身边的人牵起手来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会变得温暖  不会再冰冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是寂寞也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事也是分为好和坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位男生不要全裸冲入女澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千堂同学果然在生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家也都认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位就是今天起转入本班的支仓孝平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要提问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就单刀直入了  冲入女澡堂的感想是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把细节都说清楚  你的过错我会原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么过错不过错的  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红濑  开学第一天就迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是冰美人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓  你的座位在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是支仓孝平  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红濑桐叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始班会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想各位也都清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升到了五年级就得考虑下将来的志愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要放眼将来  建立明确的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女澡堂大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全成为名人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当作省去了自我介绍的麻烦就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不关己高高挂起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  还是得去找副会长谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  瑛里华…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  没见到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人前我又不好叫她  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是在一个学校生活啊  道歉的机会多的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阳菜种的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为我是美化委员会的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一段时间的话  杜鹃就会盛开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开满这个花坛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝平  你看那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？学生手册？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我太着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这量还真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搬到什么地方去啊  我帮你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这显然不是一个女生能搬动的量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蛮亲切的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度是理所当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没道成歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  各位请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一件商品  可是这次的主打品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍卖毕业生留下的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主打品就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起价5000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5000日元？卖得出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这个是几年前毕业的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准修智馆学院的校花  每晚都抱着睡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大概）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准修智馆学院校花已经证明了它有获得良好睡眠的功效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也请务必抱着这个可爱的布偶  获得治愈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8367日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交  8367日元获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  还真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那些卖出的钱  为寝室购置设备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是历代宿舍长延续下来的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为男生特别推荐的  绝密杂志登场…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  你们以为现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是修女闻名于世的平底锅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠木同学  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是宿舍长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  稍微有点闹过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁一只眼闭一只眼吧  玛玛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准那样叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女的洗礼名是玛尔佳丽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  所以叫玛玛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间也不早了  今天就此解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  孝平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  宿舍长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾得差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:10:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  孝平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷不丁的干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  上次不是说好了在孝平的房间开茶会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  真有男生感觉的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  要进来的话  就走正门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？孝平真蛮横啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思  打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边道歉边说打扰了  你根本没诚意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准欺负菜菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有欺负她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然阳菜泡的茶是最棒的  再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  修智馆学院之108秘密的照片  拍好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把数据给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好的  我记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（给支仓孝平同学）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  这样一来给新生用的小册子就搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到照片  小猫会高兴的「喵喵」叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小册子…  难道是为这个目的才让我照的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝平  谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  行李还真少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  因为经常搬家  只带了些必备的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶勺  研磨机之类的  必须要准备些茶会的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可用不着这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？没有可不好办  难道什么都要我们从楼上带下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…  难道打算每次都在我这里举办茶会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  太正确了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  大吉岭茶泡好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  能让你喜欢我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菜菜的泡茶手艺出众
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜  点心也拜托你准备啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸  到吃饭时间了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是新鲜的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按惯例  公布模拟测试的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你一点也不在乎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有参加过的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是不想提起的意思吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  孝平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  阳菜的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谦虚了  排名挺不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟千堂同学比就望尘莫及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  不管是综合  还是其它科目总是稳取第一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没能超越她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有数学  每次都是红濑同学稳取第一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这种情况  其解答方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要用加法原则相反的公理  就能很简单地得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它科目都是在及格线徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我感觉红濑同学是故意这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸又跑丢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  本来想送早饭给它的  却发现地面上有个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  果然那个兔子就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到它了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在上课时我看到它在窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我妹妹有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让她流泪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸逃了出来  想拜托支仓学长帮忙寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东仪学长  有话过会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？雪丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  看本小姐是如何抓到它的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  支仓同学为了小白  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你们也一起来帮她找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行  不将它打死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要声明一点  它可不是什么猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都听不出来像玩笑  也不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个四年级的女孩  这么卖命的寻找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和别人加深交情  也不会带来什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你这样说  我感觉很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸  在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有  究竟藏哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  赶不上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发  安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你  小白很担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再逃出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体自己就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是  这是…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑛里华会这么吃惊也是有原因的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓同学  看看自己的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不包扎的话可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠得那么近  没必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记应该先说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓学长  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到雪丸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  真的很感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后还是没能道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的机会却…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  还是时机不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  搭救完雪丸后是个好时机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  吃惊的样子也太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}今天真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,350)}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室一幕和过了约定时间这两件事  一直没能向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了约定时间的事先不提  浴室的事是哥哥害的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么原因  毕竟我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必须要道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  不…  我是想说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在开学典礼上也做过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是重新合好如初以及在第一天没完成的欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次由衷地欢迎你  支仓孝平同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到  修智馆学院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今后也请多…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  他的确与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪瑛里华会变得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  有件事我想问下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  就是…  副会长是那种会一见钟情的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~！又是哥哥乱说话！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生如游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是不断回到原点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尽全力摇动转盘  这次却坏掉  越过了终点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(3000,0)}第三话  千年泉


